OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784794689
OL,3,CBloomsbury book publisher wins payout
OL,4,Cin #1.1bn Anthropic copyright
OL,5,Csettlement
OL,7,FThe publisher of Harry Potter is to
OL,8,Freceive a multimillion-pound payout
OL,9,Fover a copyright settlement between
OL,10,Fthe AI startup Anthropic and thousands
OL,11,Fof authors after using pirated copies
OL,12,Fof their works to train its Claude
OL,13,Fchatbot.
OL,15,FBloomsbury, which is home to book by
OL,16,Fbestselling novelists Sarah J. Maas
OL,17,Fand Susanna Clarke as well as JK
OL,18,FRowling, is a beneficiary of the
OL,19,F$1.5bn (#1.12bn) settlement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784794689
OL,3,CBloomsbury book publisher wins payout
OL,4,Cin #1.1bn Anthropic copyright
OL,5,Csettlement
OL,7,FIt said it had 14,087 titles listed
OL,8,Fwithin the settlement, with a proposed
OL,9,Fcompensation of about $3,000 (around
OL,10,F#2,250) a title.
OL,12,FThe London-based company added that it
OL,13,Fexpects to receive the money in
OL,14,Finstalments, potentially starting in
OL,15,Fthe second half of this financial
OL,16,Fyear, with the proceeds to be shared
OL,17,Fwith authors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
