PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784794689
OL,3,CBloomsbury book publisher wins payout
OL,4,Cin #1.1bn Anthropic copyright
OL,5,Csettlement
OL,7,FDistrict Judge Araceli Martinez-Olguin
OL,8,Fsaid in a ruling on Monday that the
OL,9,Fclass-action settlement provides
OL,10,F"meaningful relief" to affected
OL,11,Fauthors and publishers.
OL,13,FAbout 91% of the more than 482,000
OL,14,Fbooks covered by the settlement have
OL,15,Fbeen claimed by authors or publishers
OL,16,Fwho are now due payment.
OL,26,@oD@\rtoD@ert
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
