OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784794689
OL,3,CBloomsbury book publisher wins payout
OL,4,Cin #1.1bn Anthropic copyright
OL,5,Csettlement
OL,7,FThe plaintiffs' attorney Justin Nelson
OL,8,Fsaid the agreement represented "the
OL,9,Flargest known copyright recovery in
OL,10,Fhistory", adding: "We look forward to
OL,11,Fmaking distributions to the class as
OL,12,Fpromptly as possible."
OL,14,FUS District Judge William Alsup
OL,15,Fgranted preliminary approval for the
OL,16,Fsettlement in San Francisco federal
OL,17,Fcourt last September before retiring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
