OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784794689
OL,3,CBloomsbury book publisher wins payout
OL,4,Cin #1.1bn Anthropic copyright
OL,5,Csettlement
OL,7,FLast summer, Alsup issued a mixed
OL,8,Fruling, finding that training AI
OL,9,Fchatbots on copyrighted books was not
OL,10,Fillegal but that Anthropic had
OL,11,Fwrongfully acquired millions of books
OL,12,Fthrough pirate websites.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
