FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1784794689
OL,3,CBloomsbury book publisher wins payout
OL,4,Cin #1.1bn Anthropic copyright
OL,5,Csettlement
OL,7,FAnthropic's deputy general counsel,
OL,8,FAparna Sridhar, described that ruling
OL,9,Fas a landmark decision showing "that
OL,10,Ftraining AI on books is fair use under
OL,11,Fcopyright law".
OL,13,F"We are pleased that more than 91% of
OL,14,Fauthors and publishers covered by the
OL,15,Fsettlement have claimed their share of
OL,16,Fthe payment, and we're looking forward
OL,17,Fto bringing this matter to a close,"
OL,18,FSridhar said in a statement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
