OL,3,CBloomsbury book publisher wins payout
OL,4,Cin #1.1bn Anthropic copyright
OL,5,Csettlement
OL,7,FBestselling thriller writer Andrea
OL,8,FBartz first brought the lawsuit with
OL,9,Ftwo other authors in 2024.
OL,11,FIt is the first major settlement in
OL,12,Fdozens of AI copyright cases still
OL,13,Fmaking their way through the courts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
